895
00:41:57,960 --> 00:41:58,520
 i tak dalje,

896
00:41:58,520 --> 00:41:59,660
 te radikalne skupine,

897
00:41:59,660 --> 00:42:02,360
 ali frontalno niko nema

898
00:42:02,360 --> 00:42:03,660
 takve mogućnosti,

899
00:42:03,660 --> 00:42:04,600
 sposobnosti,

900
00:42:04,600 --> 00:42:05,340
 sad,

901
00:42:05,340 --> 00:42:07,660
 trenutno su oni u defanzivi,

902
00:42:07,660 --> 00:42:08,600
 imaju sto problema,

903
00:42:08,600 --> 00:42:09,940
 ali dugoročno,

904
00:42:09,940 --> 00:42:11,040
 ako nas ikad,

905
00:42:11,040 --> 00:42:12,060
 iko napadne,

906
00:42:12,060 --> 00:42:13,200
 Srbi će nas napast.

907
00:42:13,200 --> 00:42:13,640
 Neće,

908
00:42:13,640 --> 00:42:15,060
