912
00:42:18,600 --> 00:42:19,320
 Zašto?

913
00:42:19,680 --> 00:42:20,400
 Jer Srbin

914
00:42:20,400 --> 00:42:22,760
 ima svoju politiku,

915
00:42:22,760 --> 00:42:24,360
 neka se ne uvrijede

916
00:42:24,360 --> 00:42:25,080
 obični ljudi,

917
00:42:25,080 --> 00:42:25,500
 normalni,

918
00:42:25,500 --> 00:42:25,780
 mnogo,

919
00:42:25,780 --> 00:42:26,740
 ja prijatelja Srba,

920
00:42:26,740 --> 00:42:27,280
 imam o,

921
00:42:27,280 --> 00:42:28,160
 ja govorim o...

922
00:42:28,160 --> 00:42:28,940
 Puno gledatelja,

923
00:42:28,940 --> 00:42:30,040
 podkaste nam i tamo.

924
00:42:30,040 --> 00:42:30,460
 Neka,

925
00:42:30,460 --> 00:42:30,820
 neka,

926
00:42:30,820 --> 00:42:31,100
 neka,

927
00:42:31,100 --> 00:42:32,360
