 Srbin 150,

932
00:42:36,380 --> 00:42:37,740
 180 godina

933
00:42:37,740 --> 00:42:39,320
 ima svoju ideologiju

934
00:42:39,320 --> 00:42:40,220
 odgarašanina,

935
00:42:40,220 --> 00:42:41,600
