949
00:43:06,020 --> 00:43:07,500
 a oni kontinuirano.

950
00:43:07,500 --> 00:43:09,000
 Srbi kontinuirano

951
00:43:09,000 --> 00:43:10,320
 protiv Hrvatske.

952
00:43:10,320 --> 00:43:12,640
 Bio je jedan period

953
00:43:12,640 --> 00:43:14,940
