00:43:22,540 --> 00:43:24,100
 Tada nas nisu napadali.

963
00:43:24,100 --> 00:43:24,660
 Međutim,

964
00:43:24,660 --> 00:43:25,760
 od 2000.

965
00:43:25,760 --> 00:43:26,460
