983
00:43:46,560 --> 00:43:47,200
 protjerali.

984
00:43:47,200 --> 00:43:48,140
 To ne spominju.

985
00:43:48,140 --> 00:43:48,660
 Znači,

986
00:43:48,660 --> 00:43:49,820
 oni svojim generacijima

