 Doma sam ja,

2181
01:14:30,820 --> 01:14:32,420
 punica,

2182
01:14:32,420 --> 01:14:33,340
 jel tako dalje,

2183
01:14:33,340 --> 01:14:34,000
 susjedi,

2184
01:14:34,000 --> 01:14:36,340
 djeca će ti bit maksimalno,

2185
01:14:36,340 --> 01:14:37,100
 sve će ti bit,

2186
01:14:37,100 --> 01:14:37,860
 apsolutno,

2187
01:14:37,860 --> 01:14:40,140
 ti se samo usredo dotoči

2188
01:14:40,140 --> 01:14:41,820
 da pomađeš ljudima

2189
01:14:41,820 --> 01:14:43,840
 kojima si dodjelen za zapovjednika,

2190
01:14:43,840 --> 01:14:45,840
 da maksimum oni te vole,

2191
01:14:45,840 --> 01:14:46,700
 oni te poštuju,

2192
01:14:46,700 --> 01:14:47,620
 oni te cijene,

2193
01:14:47,620 --> 01:14:48,700
 jer se to znalo,

2194
01:14:48,700 --> 01:14:49,980
 odmah na početku sam ja

2195
01:14:49,980 --> 01:14:50,700
 takav odnoslo.

2196
01:14:50,700 --> 01:14:52,940
 Oni u tebe vide povjerenje,

2197
01:14:52,940 --> 01:14:54,740
 ti se njima posvjeti

2198
01:14:54,740 --> 01:14:56,300
 i tvoja ti je zadača

2199
01:14:56,300 --> 01:14:57,640
 da vodiš računa

2200
01:14:57,640 --> 01:14:58,800
 o njihovim životima,

2201
01:14:58,800 --> 01:15:00,640
 a vrati se kući.

2202
01:15:00,640 --> 01:15:01,040
 Eto.

2203
01:15:01,040 --> 01:15:03,440
 I sad sam vas na kraju

2204
01:15:03,440 --> 01:15:04,080
 i razplakala.

2205
01:15:04,080 --> 01:15:05,040
 Pa niste.

2206
01:15:05,040 --> 01:15:07,780
 To je moj emotivni ovako,

2207
01:15:07,780 --> 01:15:10,660
 to je moja i blagodat

2208
01:15:10,660 --> 01:15:15,260
 i moja zapravo od Boga dana kvaliteta

2209
01:15:15,260 --> 01:15:17,560
 da mogu na pravdu,

2210
01:15:17,560 --> 01:15:19,480
 za pravdu i poginut,

2211
01:15:19,480 --> 01:15:22,700
 a za nepravdu isto ne štedit se.

2212
01:15:22,700 --> 01:15:23,600
 Borit se.

2213
01:15:23,600 --> 01:15:24,220
 Tako je.

2214
01:15:24,220 --> 01:15:25,420
 Protiv nije.

2215
01:15:25,740 --> 01:15:26,940
 Gospodine Sačiću,

2216
01:15:26,940 --> 01:15:28,080
 hvala vam na vremenu

2217
01:15:28,080 --> 01:15:29,580
 koje ste ozlojili za nas.

2218
01:15:29,580 --> 01:15:31,140
 Svako dobro vam želim.

2219
01:15:31,140 --> 01:15:32,720
 Šteta što vas nema u Sabaru.

2220
01:15:32,720 --> 01:15:35,860
 Sad će se netko i s tim porugati,

2221
01:15:35,860 --> 01:15:37,360
 odnosno izrugivati,

2222
01:15:37,360 --> 01:15:39,520
 ali ja ću reći baš je šteta što vas nema u Sabaru.

2223
01:15:39,520 --> 01:15:40,760
 Pa mnogi su mi to rekli.

2224
01:15:40,760 --> 01:15:41,540
 A šta ćete ti?

2225
01:15:41,540 --> 01:15:44,980
 Bio sam neočekivano iznenađen.

2226
01:15:44,980 --> 01:15:47,660
 Mislio sam u tom mom kraju u Zagorju.

2227
01:15:47,660 --> 01:15:51,060
 Ako svog hrvatskog sina Sačića ne poznajete,

2228
01:15:51,060 --> 01:15:54,200
 pet posto da mu dajete nakon svega da uže,

2229
01:15:54,280 --> 01:15:56,300
 pa niste ni zavrijedili onda Sačića.

2230
01:15:56,300 --> 01:15:57,620
 Niste ni zavrijedili.

2231
01:15:57,620 --> 01:15:59,600
 Hvala vam najljepši.

2232
01:15:59,600 --> 01:16:00,040
 Molim.

2233
01:16:00,040 --> 01:16:01,540
 Svako dobro vam želim.

2234
01:16:01,540 --> 01:16:04,240
 Dragi naši gledatelji podcasta Mrežnica,

2235
01:16:04,240 --> 01:16:07,000
 bio je ovo umirovljeni general Željko Sačić.

2236
01:16:07,000 --> 01:16:09,060
 Uvijek strastven, uvijek emotivan,

2237
01:16:09,060 --> 01:16:12,700
 uvijek onako na obraniku domovine.

2238
01:16:14,140 --> 01:16:15,220
 Još jedan put vama hvala.

2239
01:16:15,220 --> 01:16:17,480
 A vama, dragi naši, hvala što nas gledate.

2240
01:16:17,480 --> 01:16:18,760
 Svako dobro vam želim.

